    bibo:volume "173" ;
    dc:creator "Brown, Brian V.; Amorim, Dalton De Souza; Kung, Giar-Ann" ;
    dc:date "2015" ;
    dc:title "New morphological characters for classifying Phoridae (Diptera) from the structure of the thorax" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5333736>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5333740>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5333639> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5333736>
    dc:description "Figure 45 Character 45. Lumen of hind coxa large (0); lumen of hind coxa reduced (1). A, Javanoxenia. B, Brownphora. C, Apodicrania. D, Neopleurophora. E, Diplonevra. F, Borophaga." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5333736/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5333740>
    dc:description "Figure 46 Character 46. Posterior anepisternal crest slender (0); posterior anepisternal crest wide (1). A, Bothroprosopa. B, Epcinemis. C, Godavaria. D, Abaristophora. E, Borophaga. F, Stichillus." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5333740/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5333639>
    dc:description "Figure 13 Characters 4 and 7. Character 4 (black arrows). R4+5 ending at wing tip (0); R4+5 ending before wing tip (1); R4+5 at most at distal one-third of wing length (2). Character 7 (grey arrows). R1 reaching at least distal third of wing (0); R1 reaching distal half of wing (1); R1 reaching basal third of wing (2). A, Lindneromyia. B, Lonchoptera. C, Sciadocera. D, Chonocephalus. E, Pseudacteon. F, Coniceromyia. G. Latiborophaga. H, Trophithauma." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5333639/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

